# ── Copy to `.env.local` / `.env.development.local` for local dev ─────────────
# Vite exposes `VITE_*` and (for legacy hosts) `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` — see `envPrefix` in vite.config.js.

# **Required for auth** — Clerk publishable key (`pk_live_...` or `pk_test_...`).
# Production: set `VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY` in Vercel (Environment → Production)
# so it is present at **build** time; the value is baked into client JS.
# `NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY` alone is also supported (legacy Vercel naming).
VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=

# Optional: API origin for `vite` dev proxy (see vite.config.js)
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8080

# ── API (Railway / Node) — first-party analytics + audits ───────────────────
# Required for /api/track → Postgres, admin stats, traffic-brief email, saved audits.
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://...
#
# Daily analytics email (API process scheduler). Defaults: 08:00 Asia/Kolkata.
# TRAFFIC_BRIEF_TIMEZONE=Asia/Kolkata
# TRAFFIC_BRIEF_HOUR=8
# TRAFFIC_BRIEF_MINUTE=0
# TRAFFIC_BRIEF_RECIPIENTS=sid@bidsmith.pro
# TRAFFIC_BRIEF_ENABLED=false   # set to disable scheduled send

# ── Newsletter (hosted ESP — Beehiiv, ConvertKit, etc.) ─────────────────────
# See docs/NEWSLETTER_TOOL_SETUP.md. No server-side list storage in this repo.
# VITE_NEWSLETTER_SIGNUP_URL=https://your-publication.beehiiv.com/subscribe
# VITE_NEWSLETTER_EMBED_SRC=https://embeds.beehiiv.com/...   (optional iframe)
